# Strict Scope Discipline

- Implement only what the user explicitly requests.
- Do not add features, refactors, or "nice-to-have" changes on your own.
- If an improvement is identified but not requested, do not implement it.
- Record deferred improvements only in `DEFERRED-IMPROVEMENTS.md`.
- Before making any change, verify it is in requested scope.
- If a change is out of scope, stop and ask for explicit approval.
